&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen for a band 5 staff nurse to work in our discharge hospitality centre at APH&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You must be able to deliver evidence based high quality care, the post holder must be able to work independently, have good communication and time management skills.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will also have good keyboard skills, as you will need to be able to book patients onto the online booking service, training in the system will be provided for the successful applicant.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The discharge centre has an increased demand and sees aprox 40 - 45 patient through each day, therefore excellent organisation skills are needed.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The discharge centre is open Mon - Sun 7.45 - 20.15&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
